title: the erring private IT Park under intimation to the Directorate of Industries
clause_text: the erring private IT Park under intimation to the Directorate of Industries. This provision will also be applicable to existing IT Parks. These provisions will be over and above the penal provisions of the MRTP Act. 1966.
